        "title": "Fire Extinguishers: Foam Extinguisher",
        "content": "### Fire Extinguishers: Foam Extinguisher\n\nWeb: [www.searescue.org.za](http://www.searescue.org.za) | Tel: 021 434 4011 | Email: [bretta@searescue.org.za](mailto:bretta@searescue.org.za)\n\n#### Foam Extinguisher \u2013 Cream Label\n\n![Foam-based fire extinguisher](images/Pre-sea_Training_Course_Notes_p15_img2.jpeg)\n\nFoam extinguishers can be used on nearly all types of fires.\n\n**Advantages:**\n\n1. Very effective on plastic, rubber, petrol, and oil fires.\n2. Extinguishes through both cooling and excluding oxygen.\n\n**Disadvantages:**\n\n1. The disadvantages listed for water extinguishers (1, 3, 4, and 5) apply equally to foam extinguishers.",
