        "id": "trainee_crew_module_1_ch8",
        "title": "Lifejacket Safety and AIS MOB Devices",
        "content": "### Lifejacket Safety and AIS MOB Devices\n\nWeb: [www.searescue.org.za](http://www.searescue.org.za) | Tel: 021 434 4011 | Email: [bretta@searescue.org.za](mailto:bretta@searescue.org.za)\n\n#### Video 2: Lifejacket Test\n\n#### AIS MOB Units\nMost of our lifejackets are equipped with AIS MOB devices. These devices send out an AIS position signal when activated, allowing local AIS receivers to identify your position, thereby facilitating your rescue by removing the search element.\n\n![The AIS MOB device](images/Trainee_Crew_Module_1_p9_img3.jpeg)",
